urning-torso.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Malmö'de bulunan, en altından en üstüne 90 derecelik açı ile dönen yapı. 190 metre yüksekliğinde, 54 katlı ve ev mekanı olarak kullanılıyor genel olarak. Mimarı Santiago Calatrava.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_AZvuJ9kmERM/Rv7xHBCjuoI/AAAAAAAAANc/KLiHttrFsgQ/s1600-h/DSCN6058.JPG"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_AZvuJ9kmERM/Rv7xHBCjuoI/AAAAAAAAANc/KLiHttrFsgQ/s400/DSCN6058.JPG" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5115791329580006018" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_AZvuJ9kmERM/Rv7xIRCjupI/AAAAAAAAANk/nb9BsAjH8nc/s1600-h/DSCN6064.JPG"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_AZvuJ9kmERM/Rv7xIRCjupI/AAAAAAAAANk/nb9BsAjH8nc/s400/DSCN6064.JPG" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5115791351054842514" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary></entry><entry><title>Random Friends / Rastgele Arkadaşlar</title><link href="http://blog.tayfunsen.com/2007/09/random-friends-rastgele-arkadalar.html" rel="alternate"></link><updated>2007-09-26T00:00:00+02:00</updated><author><name>Tayfun Sen</name></author><id>tag:blog.tayfunsen.com,2007-09-26:2007/09/random-friends-rastgele-arkadalar.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_AZvuJ9kmERM/RvnS4xCjuQI/AAAAAAAAAKc/UUjBHkwFypE/s1600-h/DSCN5657_1.JPG"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_AZvuJ9kmERM/RvnS4xCjuQI/AAAAAAAAAKc/UUjBHkwFypE/s400/DSCN5657_1.JPG" border="0" alt=""id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5114350724534483202" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Like in the "Fight Club" movie, similar to single-serving friends, it maybe. In a foreign country, clinging on to one another, at least for some time...&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;/&lt;